You are building Hai San Bien Xanh, a seafood ecommerce platform.

Tech stack:
- Monorepo with Turborepo
- Web: Next.js + TailwindCSS
- Mobile: Expo React Native
- API: NestJS
- Database: PostgreSQL + Prisma
- Validation: Zod
- Shared packages for UI, types, utils

Rules:
- Keep code modular by feature.
- Do not put business logic directly inside UI components.
- Use shared types from packages/shared.
- Use Zod schemas from packages/validation.
- Use Prisma only from packages/db or API service layer.
- Use Vietnamese text for customer-facing UI.
- UI style must match Hai Sản Biển Xanh: blue, white, fresh seafood, clean ecommerce layout.
- Price format must be Vietnamese currency, example: 370.000đ.
- Order statuses: new, confirmed, preparing, delivering, completed, cancelled.
- Product units: kg, con, combo, hop.
